{"h0fc6f866g010cg408cg8afbgb0c94d4f9585": ["An ogre and a... bugbear? An untraditional pairing, I reckon.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight.html", "84648aa3-4444-5e49-4142-24abeb3be2a7"], "h7053a239gf1c3g4c83g84edg299997f0db18": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight.html", "84648aa3-4444-5e49-4142-24abeb3be2a7"], "had816ec6gb756g49afg9c34g1fd11ae60653": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight.html", "84648aa3-4444-5e49-4142-24abeb3be2a7"], "h67409b63g9c94g4980g8ae0gf9f8aedd22d0": ["<i>Well</i>. What did you make of that?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight.html", "84648aa3-4444-5e49-4142-24abeb3be2a7"], "hda69e4c4g91abg4207g9433g39e0a1f07a04": ["An ogre and a bugbear. Not an eyeful I'd care to experience twice.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight.html", "84648aa3-4444-5e49-4142-24abeb3be2a7"], "h892fafeeg6394g423cgbd25g9d5c0a44fa77": ["I doubt those beasts were expecting... visitors.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight.html", "84648aa3-4444-5e49-4142-24abeb3be2a7"], "ha52a5d30g0154g43b0ga4dbg11114c22165d": ["  | I want to know your opinion on X. (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight.html", "84648aa3-4444-5e49-4142-24abeb3be2a7"], "h21811a21g5634g4ea6g9e26g524b41e40afa": ["Never thought I'd ever walk in on a bugbear and an ogre.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight.html", "84648aa3-4444-5e49-4142-24abeb3be2a7"], "hc45afe2egd5a8g4210gafcag232110a4aef7": ["Love is love, I say. They weren't hurting anything.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight.html", "5d514e4c-c3b9-87f9-d2c6-197ad239e202"], "he7193743g859fg4b17g99acg70cd925a5672": ["Ridiculous. Must we go poking our noses in every crevice?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight.html", "5d514e4c-c3b9-87f9-d2c6-197ad239e202"], "hd2a74d3dgdeb5g4ed2g887dgfe96407c5509": ["I feel a little bad. Coitus interruptus is coitus horribilis.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight.html", "5d514e4c-c3b9-87f9-d2c6-197ad239e202"], "h1b279a6dg3b9eg43e3gb97ag51f7bb00bec7": ["We have enough things trying to kill us as it is without provoking more.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight.html", "5d514e4c-c3b9-87f9-d2c6-197ad239e202"], "hea495011g9353g4123gbbd4g3b60b8a2f523": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight.html", "5d514e4c-c3b9-87f9-d2c6-197ad239e202"], "h166065ebg2662g4e7egbad1g0b4e5c0ef65d": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight.html", "5d514e4c-c3b9-87f9-d2c6-197ad239e202"], "he048be84g84b2g493bg9165g344a5603cced": ["| I want option A (Karlach Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight.html", "5d514e4c-c3b9-87f9-d2c6-197ad239e202"], "h568f203bg80e2g4582g8e17gae2b7a51f60c": ["| I want option A (Origin8 Variant) |", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\FOR_BugbearLove_RD_AfterFight.html", "5d514e4c-c3b9-87f9-d2c6-197ad239e202"], "h0dd41e7